{"type":null,"faqId":34731,"title":" How do I set emails?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">Adding an email account</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Add account</span><span>. Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Email</span><span> to add an email account or </span><span class=\"s1\">Corporate</span><span> to add an Exchange account. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110578\" style=\"width:1.3673611in;height:2.4180555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110579\" style=\"width:1.3645834in;height:2.426389in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110580\" style=\"width:1.3569444in;height:2.4131944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110581\" style=\"width:1.3569444in;height:2.4131944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110582\" style=\"width:1.3645834in;height:2.426389in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">Manual setup:</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>On the </span><span class=\"s1\">Account setup</span><span> screen, type the account and password. </span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Manual setup</span><span>. </span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">POP3</span><span>. Set the receive server. </span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Next</span><span>. Set the send server. </span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">5.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Next</span><span>. Set the inbox checking frequency. </span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">6.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Next</span><span>. Set your name and your account name. </span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">7.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Next</span><span>. Log in to the inbox screen. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">Automatic setup: (Email parameters are preset on your phone.)</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>On the </span><span class=\"s1\">Account setup</span><span> screen, type the account and password. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>Click </span><span class=\"s1\">Next</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Next</span><span>. Set the inbox checking frequency. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Next</span><span>. Set your name and your account name. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Next</span><span>. Log in to the inbox screen. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>If no email parameters are preset, contact your email service provider. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">Sending an email</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>On the </span><span class=\"s1\">Inbox</span><span> screen, touch </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110583\" style=\"width:0.30416667in;height:0.24027778in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>. On the </span><span class=\"s1\">Compose</span><span> screen, enter the recipient, subject, and content. Touch </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110584\" style=\"width:0.27083334in;height:0.20833333in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110585\" style=\"width:1.3986111in;height:2.4826388in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">Checking and deleting emails</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>On the inbox screen, touch an email to check it or touch </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110586\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.26041666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> to delete it. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">Deleting an email account</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"_Toc378693812\"><span>On the inbox screen, </span><span>touch</span><span> the menu key and touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span>. Touch the account you want to delete and swipe to the bottom and delete it. </span></a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"9471","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436871808000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L02","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"HONOR 3C LTE (H30-L02)","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}